General.Name: Technology Metals Australia Ltd
General.Description: Technology Metals Australia Limited engages in identifying and exploring mineral projects in Australia. Its flagship project is the Murchison Technology Metals Project that comprises Gabanintha and Yarrabubba Vanadium Projects located in the mid-west region of Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
